# MagicSquare Project Baseline

## Project Intent
- Build the 4x4 MagicSquare solution with ECB architecture and TDD.
- Keep domain rules explicit in the entity layer.
- Maintain reliable automated tests with pytest.

## Repository Layout
- Production code belongs in `src/`.
- Tests belong in `tests/`.
- Prefer parallel directory layout by layer: `boundary`, `control`, `entity`.

## Working Behavior
- Before coding, review existing tests and preserve their intent.
- Identify the target ECB layer before introducing new logic.
- After coding, run relevant pytest suites first, then broaden scope if needed.
